<% base_info = JSON.parse @pt_task['torrent_base_info']%>
<div style="width: 540px;
  padding: 15px;
  border: 1px solid #B2EBF2;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  border-radius: 4px;
  -webkit-border-radius: 5px;
  font-family: 'Verdana', 'Georgia', 'Calibri', 'Serif', 'Times New Roman';
  margin:0 auto;
  background-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(top, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 60%, #fff), -webkit-linear-gradient(20deg, #e0f1ff 32%, #fffae3);
  background-image: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 60%, #fff), linear-gradient(70deg, #e0f1ff 32%, #fffae3);">
<h4>Hi, <%= @user.name %></h4>
<p style="word-break: break-all; font-size: 14px;">你添加的任务：<b><%= base_info['chsTitle'] %>（<%= base_info['engTitle'] %>）</b>已经处理完成。</p>
<p style="word-break: break-all; font-size: 14px;">你可以选择扫描二维码，或者点击下方链接观看。</p>
<p style="word-break: break-all; font-size: 14px;">二维码和链接的有效期均为三个小时，如果超过有效期，可前往<a style="outline: none;"
href="https://www.everthis.com/pt_tasks">https://www.everthis.com/pt_tasks</a>自行观看。</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
  <img style="display:inline-block;width:480px;height:480px;" src="<%= @qrcodeUrl %>" />
</p>
<p><a style="word-break: break-all; font-size: 14px;" href="<%= @signUrl %>"><%= @signUrl %></a></p>
<h1 style="text-align:center;">:)</h1>

</div>